EASTERN NORTH ATLANTIC.
SCOTLAND-WEST COAST.
HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS.
1. HAZARDOUS OPERATIONS 1000Z TO 2000Z
   DAILY 24 THRU 28 MAY WITHIN
   30 MILES OF 57-32.7N 009-22.8W.
   VESSELS INTENDING TO ENTER AREA SHOULD CONTACT
   HEBRIDES RANGE CONTROL ON VHF CH 16 FOR ADVICE.
2. CANCEL THIS MSG 282100Z MAY.
